 surfaces: clay, grass, hard, blue-green hard, classic synthetic, indoor hard and indoor synthetic; each with a specific rebound. \n- 13 tournaments: 4 Slam and 9 Masters. \n- Full ranking system. \n- Fully customizable 3D male player. ", "short_description": "First Person Tennis is the first tennis simulator developed for VR. Now, you can play on a real tennis court and face professional tennis players. You'll have to show all your technical and tactical skills."}]}, "developer_name": "Mikori Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/fptprivacypolicy/home-page", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.facebook.com/MikoriGames/", "publisher_name": "Mikori Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.facebook.com/Firstpersontennis", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SPORTS", "SIMULATION", "ACTION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["de", "ru", "en", "pt_BR", "it", "fr", "es", "ja", "zh_CN"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "3168313566780415"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 38, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1049626860183162"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1187353675903654"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "882421170344557"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1147047383289987"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "602151027929264"}, {"status": "PENDING", "id": "515302120671224"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "34218910